    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8020-a1ad-c69ccf65fc95",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Position Tracking is a potentially useful source of educational data. The paper explores how using physical positioning data can be used for Social Network Analysis purposes. Authors perform an analyzis on primary school data (98 students and 6 teachers) across 8 weeks. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8020-a1ad-c69ccf65fc95",
        "parent": {
